
### WHITE LIST trusted host names ###
/\.hotmail\.com$/	  OK
/\.google\.com$/	   OK
/\.yahoo\.[a-z]{2,3}$/		OK
/\.gmail\.com$/		OK
/\.microsoft\.com$/		OK
/\.linkedin\.com$/		OK
/\.twitter\.com$/		OK
/\.ebay\.com$/		OK
/\.paypal\.com$/		OK

### BLACK LIST untrusted host names for business ###
